    <IsekaiLeveling.SkillTree.PassiveTreeDef>
        <defName>PassiveTree_Ranger</defName>
        <label>Ranger</label>
        <treeClass>Ranger</treeClass>
        <treeDescription>Veterans of the wild who blend marksmanship with survival instinct. Five constellations radiate from the ranger's core — each honing a different edge of their deadly craft. Lock onto prey and let Predator Focus sharpen every successive shot.</treeDescription>
        <classGimmick>PredatorFocus</classGimmick>
        <classGimmickName>Predator Focus</classGimmickName>
        <classGimmickDescription>Consecutive ranged hits on the same target stack focus marks, each boosting Shooting Accuracy. Switching targets resets stacks to 1 on the new prey. Predator Focus scales along the Hawkeye Path. Tier 1 (Keen Eye): max 3 stacks, +4% accuracy each (max +12%). Tier 2 (Focused Aim): max 4 stacks, +5% each (max +20%). Tier 3 (Lethal Precision): max 5 stacks, +6% each (max +30%). Tier 4 (Apex Predator): max 7 stacks, +7% each (max +49%). Focus fire to devastate.</classGimmickDescription>

